ZH: 这座城市的土地非常富饶。
EN: The land of this city is very fertile.

ZH: 这块土地被用来种植小麦。
EN: This piece of land is used to grow wheat.

ZH: 那些农夫正在耕种土地。
EN: Those farmers are cultivating the land.

ZH: 这片土地被开发成了一座公园。
EN: This piece of land has been developed into a park.

ZH: 这个城市的土壤质量很好。
EN: The quality of the soil in this city is very good.

ZH: 农民们在土里种下了种子。
EN: Farmers planted seeds in the soil.

ZH: 这个农场的土地面积很大。
EN: The farm has a large land area.

ZH: 地震使得这块土地发生了裂变。
EN: An earthquake caused a fracture in the land.

ZH: 这片土地上有一处废弃的建筑。
EN: There is an abandoned building on this land.

ZH: 山村的土路非常崎岖。
EN: The dirt road in the mountain village is very rugged.

ZH: 冰雪覆盖着整块土地。
EN: The whole land is covered with ice and snow.

ZH: 荒漠中的土地沙尘飞扬。
EN: The land in the desert is covered in dust.

ZH: 雨后土地变得湿滑。
EN: The land becomes slippery after the rain.

ZH: 高楼大厦的基础深深扎根于土壤中。
EN: The foundation of the skyscraper is deeply rooted in the soil.

ZH: 他的父亲是一位土地投资者。
EN: His father is a land investor.

ZH: 被海水侵蚀的土地正逐渐消失。
EN: The land eroded by seawater is gradually disappearing.

ZH: 一些动物在土中挖洞找食物。
EN: Some animals dig holes in the soil to find food.

ZH: 这块土地的价值在不断上涨。
EN: The value of this land is constantly rising.

ZH: 在中国，土地是国有资产。
EN: In China, land is state-owned property.

ZH: 风和日丽的日子里，土地显得格外美丽。
EN: On sunny days, the land looks especially beautiful.
